===Current squad===
The following players were called up for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]], and for the pre-tournament friendly matches against [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao]] and [[Bolivia national football team|Bolivia]] on 30 May and 6 June 2026, respectively.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/articles/c4g94rpvx73o |title=World Cup: Scotland select Ross Stewart & Findlay Curtis in 26-man squad |website=BBC Sport |date=19 May 2026 |accessdate=19 May 2026}}</ref> Following the Curaçao match, [[Billy Gilmour]] withdrew from the squad through injury and was replaced a day later by [[Tyler Fletcher]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/articles/cn9pwg12z0lo |title=Billy Gilmour: Scotland midfielder ruled out of World Cup with knee injury |website=BBC Sport |date=30 May 2026 |accessdate=30 May 2026}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/cn8pmj99jk7o|title=Fletcher chosen to replace Gilmour in Scotland squad|publisher=[[BBC Sport]]|date=May 31, 2026|access-date=May 31, 2026}}</ref>
